      "rationale": "All five validation comparisons (stiffness and yield force at Lab 1; stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm at Lab 2) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10%. The most challenging comparison is yield force at Lab 2 (E/uval = 1.89, 9.4% difference), which remains within acceptance bounds. The validation metric framework follows ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3."
