      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the regulatory submission plan and directly correspond to the clinical performance thresholds for pedicle screw constructs. No surrogate or proxy quantities are used. The QoIs are identical between the validation activity and the COU."
    },
